==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outspeak
<hw>Out*speak"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
exceed in speaking.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To speak openly or boldly.</def> <rj><au>T.
Campbell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>To express more than.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outspeed</ent>⟦br⟧
